<br>
Thott was going for more of an overall score, while I wanted to try and break things up and define them a little more.<br>
<br>
The stacking of necro's and even shaman for that matter I didn't and don't see how I could address in a &quot;simple&quot; chart.  Both classes do not stack well with each other, but they do bring some unique class spells and skills to the table.<br>
<br>
I did think about applying weights to the numbers, but that would get even more subjective and less objective.  Someone might say Call of the Hero is worth 10 points while others would argue that it should be negative 10 points.<br>
<br>
