<br>
* Druids got a full point for having a duriable pet?  Shamans do not even get a pet until 34th lvl but they got the same point that Mages and Necros did?<br>
<br>
* Necromancers got a point for having a single AoE spell that does 104 damage?  Not really the same as a Wizard or Mages AoE ability.<br>
<br>
* Fear All is valued the same as Fear Animal?<br>
<br>
If it was scaled then you could account for such things as getting a pet later in the game or having DD that is limited to certain mob types.  Otherwise according to the chart a Necromancers DD should be equal to that of a Wizard.<br>
<br>
